welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Naranja, a charming city known for its beautiful landscapes and warm hospitality. We invite you to explore our vibrant community and experience all that Naranja has to offer. Enjoy your stay!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tamiami Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Tamiami Airport caters to private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Wifi is available throughout the airport and is free for all passengers.

terminals.name: Central Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal of Miami International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: North Terminal
terminals.description: The second largest terminal at Miami International Airport, primarily serving domestic and select international flights.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The newest terminal at Miami International Airport, serving primarily international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
